oji\" /><br />\n<br />\n遊行日期：23/11(星期六)<br />\n遊行時間：10:00a.m.<br />\n遊行地點：九龍塘沙福道》喇沙小學<br />\n<br />\n活動詳情請入Tg link : <a href=\"https://t.me/StopKillingOurKids\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FStopKillingOurKids&d=Cf%2BepIHKvYs8nB0OclbNLNagwJJ%2BwSr9lfhZhsTZPo0%3D&h=c914a6f2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/StopKillingOurKids</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Cju0269.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCju0269.jpg&h=63e6c479&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rd7aFTR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Frd7aFTR.jpg&h=ca0776ad&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/twsU7yT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtwsU7yT.jpg&h=3c84c1cb&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dY2en7e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdY2en7e.jpg&h=8a342c95&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cFArYFz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcFArYFz.jpg&h=60fb1aa6&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/r4o9b0A.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fr4o9b0A.jpg&h=8e8a1485&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cnHU7yW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcnHU7yW.jpg&h=e75d6ebc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n連登原post :<br />\n(家長x小朋友x教育工作者)23/11 保護小朋友遊行<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1744011\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1744011</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"933761226b9e6d28bd28a3ef7196371b004d4a7e","tid":1741341,"uid":209657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T13:15:24.000Z","msg":"我個肚好痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f4f0e390f0df36194898f73218faaa431cf7c85","tid":1